{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body><p class=\"_page_ _page_1 read-full\">\n濕疹戒口！有濕疹人士要特別注意飲食，留意中醫師提到的濕疹戒口食物，尤其是蝦、蟹和糖這類增加濕熱的食物，不想濕疹惡化，就盡量忍口，不要吃這些濕疹食物啦，仲有注意生活上的小習慣！\n</p>\n \n<div class=\"_more_content_\">\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_2\">\n<p>Text : Moyin｜Photo : 新傳媒資料室｜營養顧問：何庭軒中醫師</p>\n<h2>9大濕疹戒口食物</h2>\n<p>俗語有云：禍從口出，但原來也有禍從口入。除了天氣會影響濕疹外，飲食方面也要特別注意，切記濕疹戒口！（備註：文中為參考圖片）</p>\n\n<p>酒為濕熱之物，亦為發物，即富有營養而令某些疾病加重的食物，飲後會增加人體濕熱之性，令濕疹加重。</p>\n<img alt=\"濕疹\" data-src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/nhv4dxh3MJN7gxp/wk1_183844392259e87904c363b.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"965\">濕疹要戒口的食物，啤酒類飲品！\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_3\">\n<h2>2. 芋頭</h2>\n<p>芋頭黏滯，古籍中亦明言生吃有毒，即使煮熟，食用後也容易導致滯肚，阻礙脾臟的去濕功能，使人體之濕毒更難消除，助長濕疹。</p>\n<img alt=\"容易導致滯肚的芋頭，也少吃為妙。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/nhv4dxh3MJN7gxp/wk.2jpg_28623777159e87926a2b74.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"803\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"1200\">容易導致滯肚的芋頭，也少吃為妙。\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_4\">\n<h2>3.糯米</h2>\n<p>糯米性溫，多食令人濕熱，與芋頭一樣，亦是黏滯之物，容易加重人體濕熱之性，除濕疹外，患有口腔或皮膚潰瘍、甲狀腺腫大者亦應避免食用。</p>\n<img alt=\"糯米多食會濕熱，濕疹人士忌吃。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/nhv4dxh3MJN7gxp/wk4_17271470159e879427e624.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"1200\">糯米多食會濕熱，濕疹人士忌吃。\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_5\">\n<h2>4. 牛奶</h2>\n<p>不少研究已經指出，大部分亞洲人均無法消化牛奶中的主要成分，所以很多人飲用牛奶及奶類製品後會出現消化不良、腹瀉，甚至過敏等不適。大部分濕疹患者皆是過敏體質，故不建議服用牛奶。</p>\n<img alt=\"濕疹患者如果是過敏體質，要避免牛奶及奶類製品。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/nhv4dxh3MJN7gxp/wk5_179141748159e87950f2e0a.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"393\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"236\">濕疹患者如果是過敏體質，要避免牛奶及奶類製品。\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_6\">\n<p> </p>\n\n<p>蝦蟹性味極為寒涼，容易損害脾胃功能，除腹痛腹瀉等不適外，亦使脾胃去濕的能力受損，而且海產類食物容易惹濕，故往往使本身症狀加重之餘，亦更難治療。</p>\n<img alt=\"蝦、蟹極為寒涼，容易損害脾胃去濕的能力，濕疹人士要避免！\" data-src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/nhv4dxh3MJN7gxp/wk3_58795769959e8795e42881.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"1200\">蝦、蟹極為寒涼，容易損害脾胃去濕的能力，濕疹人士要避免！\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_7\">\n<h2>6. 高麗參、鹿茸等大補之物</h2>\n<p>不少人也知道濕疹患者屬虛實錯雜的體質，便打算自行進補。其實濕疹患者最忌便是補，即使是中醫師開方，也要非常謹慎。</p>\n<img alt=\"濕疹患者最忌便是進補！進食高麗參、鹿茸等補品，建議先詢問醫生。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/nhv4dxh3MJN7gxp/wk6_144741874059e8796bbcae8.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"1200\">濕疹患者最忌便是進補！進食高麗參、鹿茸等補品，建議先詢問醫生。\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_8\">\n\n<p>榴槤性溫，且有補火助陽的功效。對於身體有明顯積熱的濕疹患者，榴槤會進一步加重積熱，使濕疹一發不可收拾。</p>\n<img alt=\"榴槤會進一步加重積熱，濕疹人士戒口！\" data-src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/nhv4dxh3MJN7gxp/wk7_182441275859e879968b0cc.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"827\">榴槤會進一步加重積熱，濕疹人士戒口！\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_9\">\n<h2>8. 麵粉製品、甜品</h2>\n<p>現代的麵粉製品含有不少添加物，大多亦含有牛奶，對濕疹患者非常不利。如果是自家製作的，也必須注意砂糖量不可太多，因為砂糖、甜品都是濕疹忌吃的，除了會加重濕邪，也容易滯胃。</p>\n<img alt=\"甜品如蛋糕、多糖類製品也要戒口，以防濕疹加劇。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/nhv4dxh3MJN7gxp/wk8_67131253659e879b20782b.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1068\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"1200\">甜品如蛋糕、多糖類製品也要戒口，以防濕疹加劇。\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_10\">\n<h2>9.辛辣刺激食物</h2>\n<p>不要吃葱、大蒜、生薑、辣椒、花椒等辛辣刺激的食物。耗陰助陽，對濕疹是一種刺激，應該避免食用。</p>\n<img alt=\"切記少吃辛辣刺激食物！\" data-src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/mg_9957_13076750105d1f45dee5efa_4951062495f7ad8f66686f-1024x683.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"960\">切記少吃辛辣刺激食物！\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_11\">\n<p>濕疹戒口係好麻煩，但為了自己的皮膚，也要努力循從！睇埋以下濕疹人士能吃的食物，煲煲湯水，多喝去濕！</p>\n\n<h2>濕疹的生活迷思</h2>\n<h2>迷思1：如何從生活習慣上改善濕疹？</h2>\n<p>首先要培養早睡早起，在熟睡中人體有自行修復的能力，所以千萬不要捱夜。</p>\n<img alt=\"早睡早起，切忌捱夜。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/nhv4dxh3MJN7gxp/03_29724411059e89d84831e5.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"801\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"1200\">早睡早起，切忌捱夜。\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_12\">\n<p>避免使用任何含有化學成分或染料的物品。</p>\n<img alt=\"少接觸化學品\" data-src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/nhv4dxh3MJN7gxp/6_44472976759e89d89268f4.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"800\">少接觸化學品\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_13\">\n<p>濕疹患者應避免浸溫泉、使用公共浴室或游泳池等，免受感染。</p>\n<img alt=\"避免浸溫泉或公共泳池。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/nhv4dxh3MJN7gxp/5805_24902327459e89d8c27b84.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"1200\">避免浸溫泉或公共泳池。\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_14\">\n<p>另外，因為寵物的毛髮是最普遍的致敏原之一，所以並不建議患有各種皮膚病的人士養寵物。</p>\n<img alt=\"濕疹人士養寵物前要考慮清楚！\" data-src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/nhv4dxh3MJN7gxp/301_16779296659e87c81a76ec.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"800\">濕疹人士養寵物前要考慮清楚！\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_15\">\n<h2>迷思2：有甚麼食療可以改善？</h2>\n<p>多吃蔬菜或飲用蔬菜汁，如檸檬、柑桔、青蘋果等都有清肝去濕的功用。</p>\n<img alt=\"少肉多菜\" data-src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/nhv4dxh3MJN7gxp/6-1_133985603059e89d87b1ad0.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"776\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"1200\">少肉多菜\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_16\">\n<img alt=\"多飲用蔬菜汁，建議選用檸檬、青蘋果，此類水果具清肝功效。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/nhv4dxh3MJN7gxp/03b_214460997959e89d86466eb.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"780\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"1200\">多飲用蔬菜汁，建議選用檸檬、青蘋果，此類水果具清肝功效。\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_17\">\n<p>另外，紅菜頭或汁生吃最可以清除體內積熱，又能補血養血，清肝護肝，非常適合長期濕疹患者。</p>\n<img alt=\"紅菜頭有益！最大功效可以清除體內積熱，濕疹人士多吃有益。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/nhv4dxh3MJN7gxp/301-1_55334358459e87c8d7100b.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"800\">紅菜頭有益！最大功效可以清除體內積熱，濕疹人士多吃有益。\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_18\">\n<h2>迷思3：甚麼人易患濕疹？</h2>\n<h2>環境因素</h2>\n<p>香港本處於中國南方，氣候潮濕炎熱，容易引起各種濕熱病患。飲食上，香港人多肉少菜，更經常吃燒烤或煎炸食物，都增加患上濕疹的機會。</p>\n<img alt=\"飲食上，香港人多肉少菜，更經常吃燒烤或煎炸食物，都增加患上濕疹的機會。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/nhv4dxh3MJN7gxp/re_001_46791664359e87c9ca2fda.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"799\">飲食上，香港人多肉少菜，更經常吃燒烤或煎炸食物，都增加患上濕疹的機會。\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_19\">\n<h2>家居衛生</h2>\n<p>居住環境潮濕，又不注重家居衛生，則更加容易罹患濕疹。濕疹是最折磨人的疾病之一，外表不討好，自身亦極不舒服，但只要把握飲食法則，注意起居，濕疹一樣可以根治！</p>\n<img alt=\"家居衛生要多留意！\" data-src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/nhv4dxh3MJN7gxp/12_868b_skincare_40701107959e89d8aa3037.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"801\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"1200\">家居衛生要多留意！\n</div>\n<div class=\"_page_ _page_20\">\n<img alt=\"何庭軒中醫師＠如意堂 香港中文大學中醫學理學碩士，現為廣州中醫藥大學博士研究生。\" data-src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/nhv4dxh3MJN7gxp/add_photo_1808334259e879f832da4.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"798\">何庭軒中醫師＠如意堂<br/> 香港中文大學中醫學理學碩士，現為廣州中醫藥大學博士研究生。\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"qa_box\" onclick=\"toggleFAQ(this)\">\n<p class=\"question\">香港18區美食有甚麼推介？</p>\n<p class=\"answer\">新假期編輯已經為你整合了香港18區美食指，其中包括尖沙咀、旺角、銅鑼灣等……即睇更多詳情。<br/>\n</p>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-25T01:06:20.597305+00:00","quality":{"score":3,"chars":1724,"images":19,"source":"WeekendHK","fallback":"none"}}